    - Hover effect to show buttons.
        -Button to copy color code.
         -
 2. 
    -Color selection screen for choosing color and saving it.
         - Color selector.
        - Color sliders (Hue,Saturation,Lightness).
     
 -Function to define the opening location for the Color selection screen.
 -Function to change the div color for the chosen color.
